          <span class="greyText">&nbsp;&middot;&nbsp;</span>
          <a class="lightGreyText" title="Hardcover 9780008150822" href="/book/show/37274039-pieces-of-her">review of another edition</a>


        

          <div class="uitext greyText bookshelves">
            Shelves:
              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/review/list/7397330-sara-sarawithoutanh?shelf=2018">2018</a>
